{"sn46.17:0.1":"Samyutta Nikaya 46.17 ","sn46.17:0.2":"2. Gilanavagga ","sn46.17:0.3":"Parangamasutta ","sn46.17:1.1":"“Sattime, bhikkhave, bojjhanga bhavita bahulikata apara param gamanaya samvattanti. ","sn46.17:1.2":"Katame satta? ","sn46.17:1.3":"Satisambojjhango …pe… upekkhasambojjhango—","sn46.17:1.4":"ime kho, bhikkhave, satta bojjhanga bhavita bahulikata apara param gamanaya samvattantiti. ","sn46.17:2.1":"Appaka te manussesu, ","sn46.17:2.2":"ye jana paragamino; ","sn46.17:2.3":"Athayam itara paja, ","sn46.17:2.4":"tiramevanudhavati. ","sn46.17:3.1":"Ye ca kho sammadakkhate, ","sn46.17:3.2":"dhamme dhammanuvattino; ","sn46.17:3.3":"Te jana paramessanti, ","sn46.17:3.4":"maccudheyyam suduttaram. ","sn46.17:4.1":"Kanham dhammam vippahaya, ","sn46.17:4.2":"sukkam bhavetha pandito; ","sn46.17:4.3":"Oka anokamagamma, ","sn46.17:4.4":"viveke yattha duramam. ","sn46.17:5.1":"Tatrabhiratimiccheyya, ","sn46.17:5.2":"hitva kame akincano; ","sn46.17:5.3":"Pariyodapeyya attanam, ","sn46.17:5.4":"cittaklesehi pandito. ","sn46.17:6.1":"Yesam sambodhiyangesu, ","sn46.17:6.2":"samma cittam subhavitam; ","sn46.17:6.3":"Adanappatinissagge, ","sn46.17:6.4":"anupadaya ye rata; ","sn46.17:6.5":"Khinasava jutimanto, ","sn46.17:6.6":"te loke parinibbuta”ti. ","sn46.17:6.7":"Sattamam. "}